{
  "stem": "26022.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So we had no money to pay storage in the United States.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we got the card, my mother and I, after my father left, that within 24 hours, we had to leave the place.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then we were sent to a so-called Jew house, and we didn't have much to move because the furniture was gone already, and much of our clothes was in the lift van because we were supposed to leave on September the sixth, mother and I.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Father left on August 18th.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He got a-- a visa to go to England until he can go to the United States, which he thought would be two, three weeks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And mother and I would then join.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Mother had the power of attorney and was going to close up and wait for the quota to be due on September the sixth.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had very little when we moved to the Jew house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, the war broke out on the second, and we never came to the United States on the sixth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's another long story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were there until June '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was leading up to something-- yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were living in the Jew house, and two SS-- that's the black uniform.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's one notch more scary than the brown.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The black uniform came up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother was at her sister's, and I was home alone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Ja?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mitkommen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Come along.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't ask whether I was the one with the power of attorney or not.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What they really wanted was my mother, who had the power of attorney.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
